<br>
Days later she arrived in Themiscrya, she smiled at the sight. Although the grounds were covered in snow, her firelite tree was still burning and bearing fruit for her sisters. She smiled seeing it proud of her gift to them.<br>
<br>
&quot;I could never let my sisters suffer.&quot;<br>
<br>
She then smiled as she greeted her sisters while walking to Hippolyte's Hut. She glanced around the Village at all the preparation they had done for the winter. It was nothing less than amazing. She finally reached Hippolyte's hut and smiled to the Amazon Guarding her door.<br>
<br>
&quot;Please tell the Queen that Alysia of Scynthia is here to speak with her on great news.&quot;<br>
<br>
The Amazon Guard smiled and nodded stepping into the hut slowly. &quot;My Queen? Alysia of Scynthia is here to speak with you. She says she has great news.&quot;<br>
<br>
Aly smiled not being able to wait to tell Hippolyte.<br>
( BTW, this is taking place before Aly sent out the scroll about her and Eli )<br>
